title: DXBallCollection.rar
description:
Description
Enjoy.

The full retail versions (works online!) of Rival Ball and DX Ball 2, along with all boardsets.

Also includes the classic DX-Ball 1 (freeware).

And seeing as it fits, this includes Super DX Ball Deluxe - the new and improved version of the Classic DX Ball.

SECRETS FOR SUPER DX-BALL DELUXE:

Click the spinning ball at the main screen to unlock DX-Ball 1 boards
Click the words "Mega Ball" on the main screen to unlock the Amiga Megaball boards.

IF THIS BECOMES OUTDATED, just copy/paste the Rivalball boards into the folder of the new version.

Yes, I actually bought these, but I'm going to be nice and save you all $200+.
